    "LLMs act as recommender systems through taskspecific prompts, while LLMs provide response and feedback to optimize prompts.",
    "In this section, we present our proposed LLM-RS with two important components, namely LLMs and prompts.",
    "Generally speaking, the rich world knowledge and general capabilities of LLMs demonstrate the potential to develop LLM-based recommender systems.",
    "Nevertheless, it is essential to introduce appropriate prompting engineering to provide domain-specific knowledge on recommendation tasks for LLMs to serve as personalized recommenders.",
    "In the following, we first describe our general framework by defining several key elements (Section 3.1)."
